Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:02.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:08.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle between the Alliance and Oracion \NSeis over Nirvana has finally come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But waiting for us at the end were \Na number of tearful farewells...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Hades?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you are aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:58.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About what, Ultear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That the Alliance has defeated \NOracion Seis, and destroyed Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:08.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, impressive indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But our goal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:11.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To locate and obtain the \Nkeys to resurrecting Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:19.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter whether Nirvana \Nis in the picture or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:28.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I have a feeling that \Nsomething far greater is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some great disruption that will \Nturn the world on its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:35.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rare, from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Swaying in the sea breeze feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this great, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Transportation is a wonderful thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Troia will wear off soon, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:02.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Troia is magic that cures motion sickness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cast it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:10.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do it over and over again, \Nit'll get less effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, you and Wendy are really \Ncoming with us to Fairy Tale, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:22.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just coming along because \NWendy said she was going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call of the Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle over, we each \Nreturned to our own guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the next wonderful \Nparfum, Erza-san, Lucy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come hang out at our place next time, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll present you with the ultimate night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give my regards to Master Makarov!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey, do something about \Nthat stripping fetish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:04.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Should we just let this go by?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'll be lonely or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They llllike each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to our own guilds...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in my hands are three new keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The contract has been broken \Nnow that Angel's been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we want {\i1}you{\i0} to be our new owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're asking too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:44.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three more friends from the 12 \NZodiac Gates, just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:49.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just tools for you to use. We?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:53.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've decided not to think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all look like people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:59.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against treating you like objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're happy to be with you, Owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm happy to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpio, Aries, Gemini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:15.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... I've gained a \Nlot more precious friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:22.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, that's why I've invited \NWendy and Carla to join Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a girl Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:28.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:41.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This area should be \Npeaceful now, for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, I bid Wendy \Nand Carla a hearty welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu-chan, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:55.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you... Always making a fuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:57.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed they're all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's getting more and \Nmore out of our league...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia was so very, very worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia's eyes pour with tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey, stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there was this \Nsnake flying in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Snakes can't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:27.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do? I'm Mirajane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful, Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real Mirajane-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:37.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that Carla is the same as Happy, \Nbut what kind of magic do you use, Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Lumping me in with the he-cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Sky Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Sky Dragon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they don't believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, awesome!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dragon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:09.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Gajeel, that means our \Nguild has three Dragon Slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's such rare magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all Dragon Slayers, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one without a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we're having a celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A party to welcome Wendy and Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Live it up! Live it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama, you didn't \Ncheat or anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, do you want my fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This place sure is fun, Carla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a request that strikes your fancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are just so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:41.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be difficult to go on \Nyour own for your first job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be a good idea to go with \Nsomeone else as an assistant, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although you'll only receive \Na portion of the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but for these bunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Wendy decide on a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. She said she decided to \Ngo with someone else at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you went with \NNatsu on your first job, Lu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to that, I've been put in \Nsituations where even infinite lives wouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a lot of fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a week \Nsince I came to Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:29.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking I should do \Nmy first job pretty soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come with Shadow Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to, then how about with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:39.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But you just said that \Nyou never had enough lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take turns then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:44.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who goes first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I \Nhaven't seen you for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:04.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a crazy story, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody outside the city \Nsays she's seen a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some incredible info, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:27.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon? Is it Igneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know those details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you meet the person who saw the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:36.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard the rumors going around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:43.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone named "Daphne" talks like \Nshe knows all about dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just that she's seen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like she actually {\i1}met{\i0} one recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It might pay to find out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:11:01.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the wilderness to the \Nwest, at an Inn named "Rise".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That dragon might be Grandine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:13.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You comin' too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obviously a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And how many times have you \Nsaid that and gotten tricked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:29.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stories about dragons are for luring people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being used!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try learning a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:36.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see yours too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see Metalicana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:43.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He just disappeared without sayin' nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:51.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's like that, but \Nhe really misses him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:56.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's Grandine, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think you shouldn't get your hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:08.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the decent tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like this delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:34.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're choosing \Nanother pretty cake today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We have a cute new recruit, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of getting it for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you chose it to suit her, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:45.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you handle 50 of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:46.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have 50 newcomers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,49 of them are for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:56.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... sense it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the traveler's inn, Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of beat-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fully-automatic lacrima-based \Ninn management system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:08.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Check-in, check-out... This little \Nthing takes care of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why there's no staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:15.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No staff, sure. But I don't \Nsee any customers either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Gray... It was a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon to decide that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone might be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we check each room individually?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:32.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:41.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, what's with this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:51.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, nobody's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last place to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this was the most suspicious \Nplace by far anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:02.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:06.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you this Daphne person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:13.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes. I am Daphne-san, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd like to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes! Talk, yes? Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be? Even if it \Nisn't! You're a customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, come in, come in, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:36.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I travel from place to place, the master \Nof spreading beauty around the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am named Daphne!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:46.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not "B" as in "beat up"! "B" as in \N"beautiful", "B" as in "beauty", "B" as in "babealicious"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what am I selling, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The diet food of your wildest dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:54.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it Metamo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Metabo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:01.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful to say the name properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not Metabo-chan! Metamo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I created it after long, \Nlong years of research!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is truly a miraculous food product!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:09.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the detoxifying bounty of the ocean and \Npickle it for 3 days and nights in secret medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:16.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then dry them out under \Nthe sun for another week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you have...? You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:22.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The diet food of your wildest \Ndreams, Metamo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it properly this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:28.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a sample since you \Nmade me so happy, little kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not overweight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes, it's quite delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one bite and your skin will shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another bite and your indigestion is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two brother and sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:43.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up, boys and girls and \Nkitties! Eat my Metamo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:48.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at how effective it \Nis in this before-and-after!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:51.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's super-effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you so impressed by?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:58.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let me read the opinions \Nof a few satisfied customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, from a Janruka-san who lives in Onibus:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I've started eating \Nthem, I've seen amazing results!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:06.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I reached my goal weight in only ten days!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:07.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, about my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No diet magic ever worked, \Nbut Metamo-chan is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:16.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes. I have quite a lot \Nmore satisfied customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying "yes-yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come here to talk about diet pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes! They aren't pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Metamo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk about Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes... Dragons, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogladyouasked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:32.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even dragons can lose \Nweight with Metamo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:33.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how amazing it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:35.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Dragon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for a dragon named \NIgneel that disappeared 7 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's searching for one named Grandine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:53.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've met with one, please tell us which \None, where you met, and when you met them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that could requip?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:04.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there are others who \Ncan use requip-style magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what worries me is the smell of \Nthe one who attacked me suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the smell of a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:17.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't sense human breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be some weird group at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they will show themselves eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should not fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:29.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, just leave things as they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:33.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should take precautions, but it is \Nnot something to worry yourself over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:38.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wants to do battle with \Nyou, it will appear again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful too, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, Natsu... You two should...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:52.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama went off somewhere \Nand didn't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard I met a dragon then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a lie to help sales!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel was spot on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:16.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if I said that Metamo-chan had \Npowder ground from the scales of a dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the sales would skyrocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scales?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes, but of course it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could I get dragon scales, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:25.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But my creations are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:30.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:34.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's a satisfied customer, \Nand will you be too, Mr. Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The floor's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are birds in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:56.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a magic barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely flames you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Salamander, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's acting differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:13.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for a customer \Nlike you... A Dragon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes... You'll understand soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry flavor no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:28.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about wasabi flavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want any!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The outside world is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely trapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite impressive magic, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blast this magic to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:50.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look at you, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come in from, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This info you got was a sham!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong \Nwith this Daphne chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Gray Fullbuster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, she llllikes him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:28.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:33.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... We've gone at it a whole \Nbunch of times, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:39.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking... Maybe it's time we \Nfinally settled this, once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I've been bringing \Nmyself down to your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:48.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:51.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do things my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sticking with you any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes, just as you heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.84,0:22:00.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray Fullbuster is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want that Dragon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:08.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, you're acting weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:16.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:58.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you is stronger? You or Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:23:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:01.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never lose to that pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:06.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Gray just said he'll \Nnever lose to that hothead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:09.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That droopy-eyed, naked...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That droopy-eyed, naked, \Nwalking giant-boxers bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:13.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaaay too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Natsu vs. Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Longer isn't better, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to make it more compact!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:21.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's just go with "pervert"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blunt, but effective.
